Results.ReviewText: I bought a jar of Nesacfe gold blend  last week and I am really enjoying it . I don't drink a lot of coffee  but I think this  is lovely and refreshing.

Results.ReviewText: I got this for work as I wanted to cut down on my caffeine intake, I wasn't expecting it to taste as good though, it's the best of both worlds in a cup

Results.ReviewText: Nescafé gold blend decaff coffee makes a really smooth rich tasting drink. It is the best on the market in my opinion and i wouldn't buy anything else.

Results.ReviewText: Just started buying this due to the recent promotions on tv. we find the taste lovely and rich and is definitely the best coffee we have ever tasted.

Results.ReviewText:
A excellent tasting Coffee! With a great smooth taste!
From one of the best producers of coffee.
You can not even tell that it is decaffeinated!

Results.ReviewText: recently switched to decaf, have tried lots but my search is now over. this is the ONE. Dont leave this one on the shelf, place it in the trolly
